Description: Hello,I have a used Fender American Original 50's Stratocaster for sale.This guitar is slightly relice'd..... I sanded down the back of the neck just a little to take off some of that sticky finish and started to do some of the fret area. Feels nice and smooth now. I also replaced the nut with a new bone nut, being that the original one was defective. Dulled the back plate. Filing marks in neck behind the nut. This guitar has a very light nitro finish therefore it dings very easily as you can see in the photo's. Comes with the original tweed hardshell case, trem arm and all the paperwork. Setup with 10's and trem is set to the body.
